channel.title: Comments on: What if The Beatles had written “Stairway to Heaven?”

item.title: By: Michael King
item.dc:creator: Michael King
item.description:
This song was off an album full of Stairway to Heaven covers. All of the songs were performed for an Australian comedy show called The Money Or The Gun starring Andrew Denton. I had a copy of this album a long time ago but have since misplaced it. It was fantastic.
http://www.amazon.com/Stairways-Heaven-Various-Artists/dp/B000005J65
